%20is%20when%20the%20buildings%20shall%20be%20brought%20down.%20Our%20bomb%20vests%20are%20blessed%20by%20the%20Prophet%20Muhammad.%20They%20shall%20not%20fail%20their%20goal.%20Our%20children%20are%20brave%20servants%20of%20Allah.%20They%20shall%20complete%20their%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20mail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20South%20East%20Delhi%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%20Ravi%20Kumar%20Singh%20said%20that%20as%20many%20as%2030%20schools%20across%20Delhi%20received%20hoax%20bomb%20threat%20emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DCP%20said%20that%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20fake%20threats%20revealed%20that%20the%20e-mails%20sent%20to%20the%20schools%20had%20been%20generated%20outside%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20receiving%20the%20information%2C%20schools%20were%20evacuated%20and%20the%20Bomb%20Disposal%20Squad%20carried%20out%20checks%20at%20the%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threatening%20emails%20raised%20concerns%20among%20parents%20and%20staff%2C%20though%20the%20police%20assured%20that%20investigations%20are%20ongoing%20and%20safety%20remains%20their%20priority.%20No%20explosives%20or%20hazardous%20materials%20have%20been%20found%20in%20any%20of%20the%20schools%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20instance%20of%20such%20threats%20disrupting%20schools%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20underlining%20the%20need%20for%20robust%20security%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20schools%20that%20received%20the%20threats%20on%20Friday%2C%20included%20the%20Bhatnagar%20Public%20School%20in%20Paschim%20Vihar%2C%20Cambridge%20School%20in%20Srinivaspuri%2C%20Delhi%20Public%20School%20in%20East%20of%20Kailash%2C%20and%20Delhi%20Public%20School%20in%20Defence%20Colony.%20Earlier%2C%20over%2040%20schools%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20received%20bomb%20threats%20via%20e-mail%20demanding%20a%20ransom%20of%20USD%2030%2C000.%20This%20email%20came%20on%20December%208%20at%20around%201