ars%20later%2C%20Musk%20left%20OpenAI%20and%20founded%20another%20rival%20start-up%2C%20xAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Musk%20alleged%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fai%2Felon-musk-escalates-legal-feud-with-sam-altman-alleges-openai-a-monopolist-7025722%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20is%20a%20monopolist%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuchir%20Balaji%20Said%20OpenAI%20Broke%20Copyright%20Law%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Suchir%20Balaji%20had%20alleged%20that%20OpenAI%20was%20violating%20copyright%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20believe%20what%20I%20believe%2C%20you%20have%20to%20just%20leave%20the%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F10%2F23%2Ftechnology%2Fopenai-copyright-law.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20technologies%20like%20ChatGPT%20were%20damaging%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20social%20media%20post%20on%20X%20in%20October%2C%20Balaji%20had%20also%20written%20about%20fair%20use%20and%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20experience%20of%20working%20at%20OpenAI%20for%20four%20years%2C%20including%20his%20work%20on%20ChatGPT%20for%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20Balaji%20concluded%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfair%20use%20seems%20like%20a%20pretty%20implausible%20defense%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20generative%20AI%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20initially%20didn't%20know%20much%20about%20copyright%2C%20fair%20use%2C%20etc.%20but%20became%20curious%20after%20seeing%20all%20the%20lawsuits%20filed%20against%20GenAI%20companies.%20When%20I%20tried%20to%20understand%20the%20issue%20better%2C%20I%20eventually%20came%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20fair%20use%20seems%20like%20a%20pretty%20implausible%20defense%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20generative%20AI%20products%2C%20for%20the%20basic%20reason%20that%20they%20can%20create%20substitutes%20that%20compete%20with%20the%20data%20they're%20trained%20on%20(sic)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20recently%20participated%20in%20a%20NYT%20story%20about%20fair%20use%20and%20generative%20AI%2C%20and%20why%20I'm%20skeptical%20%26quot%3Bfair%20use%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20a%20plausible%20defense%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20generative%20AI%20products.%20I%20also%20wrote%20a%20blog%20post%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FxhiVyCk2Vk%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FxhiVyCk2Vk%3C%2Fa%3E)%20about%20the%20nitty-gritty%20details%20of%20fair%20use%20and%20why%20I%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Suchir%20Balaji%20(%40suchirbalaji)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuchirbalaji%2Fstatus%2F1849192575758139733%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsuchir.net%2Ffair_use.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Balaji%20explained%20the%20four%20factors%20that%20determine%20whether%20generative%20AI%20qualifies%20for%20fair%20use%20or%20not.%20Among%20the%20four%20factors%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Ceffect%20of%20the%20use%20upon%20the%20potential%20market%20for%20or%20value%20of%20the%20copyrighted%20work%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fair%20use%20test%20also%20looks%20at%20the%20purpose%20and%20character%20of%20the%20use%20and%20nature%20of%20the%20copyrighted%20work%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20is%20creative%20work%20that%20is%20highly%20protected%20by%20copyright%20or%20factual%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalaji%20concluded%2C%20%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20the%20four%20factors%20seem%20to%20weigh%20in%20favor%20of%20ChatGPT%20being%20a%20fair%20use%20of%20its%20training%20da