tralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Findia-vs-australia-live-score-3rd-test-match-day-1-ind-vs-aus-live-scorecard-updates-7242619%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20vs%20Australia%20LIVE%20Score%3A%20The%20rain%20in%20Brisbane%20is%20still%20going%20on%20and%20the%20start%20of%20the%20second%20session%20has%20been%20delayed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Findia-vs-australia-live-score-3rd-test-match-day-1-ind-vs-aus-live-scorecard-updates-7242619%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BInconvenient%26quot%3B%3A%20Trump%20Plans%20To%20End%20'Costly'%20Daylight%20Saving%20Time%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20Friday%20he%20would%20work%20to%20end%20the%20%26quot%3Binconvenient%26quot%3B%20custom%20of%20moving%20clocks%20forward%20one%20hour%20every%20spring%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20imposing%20an%20unnecessary%20financial%20burden%20on%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Republican%20Party%20will%20use%20its%20best%20efforts%20to%20eliminate%20Daylight%20Saving%20Time%2C%20which%20has%20a%20small%20but%20strong%20constituency%2C%20but%20shouldn't!%20Daylight%20Saving%20Time%20(DST)%20is%20inconvenient%2C%20and%20very%20costly%20to%20our%20Nation%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20posted%20on%20his%20website%2C%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDST%20was%20adopted%20by%20the%20federal%20government%20during%20World%20War%20I%20but%20was%20unpopular%20with%20farmers%20rushing%20to%20get%20produce%20to%20morning%20markets%2C%20and%20was%20quickly%20abolished.%20Many%20states%20experimented%20with%20their%20own%20versions%20but%20it%20wasn't%20reintroduced%20nationwide%20until%201967.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Democratic-controlled%20US%20Senate%20advanced%20a%20bill%20in%202022%20that%2C%20like%20Trump's%20plan%2C%20would%20bring%20an%20end%20to%20the%20twice-yearly%20changing%20of%20clocks%2C%20in%20favor%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%2C%20permanent%20standard%20time.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20The%20Sunshine%20Protection%20Act%20called%20for%20the%20opposite%20switch%20--%20moving%20permanently%20to%20DST%20rather%20than%20eliminating%20it%20--%20to%20usher%20in%20brighter%20evenings%2C%20and%20fewer%20journeys%20home%20in%20the%20dark%20for%20school%20children%20and%20office%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20never%20made%20it%20to%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20desk%2C%20as%20it%20was%20not%20taken%20up%20in%20the%20Republican-led%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20been%20introduced%20in%202021%20by%20a%20Republican%2C%20Florida%20Senator%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%20who%20is%20about%20to%20join%20the%20incoming%20Trump%20administration%20as%20secretary%20of%20state.%20He%20said%20studies%20had%20shown%20a%20permanent%20DST%20could%20benefit%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20changing%20to%20one%20permanent%20time%20would%20put%20an%20end%20to%20Americans%20pushing%20their%20clocks%20forward%20in%20the%20spring%2C%20then%20setting%20them%20back%20an%20hour%20in%20the%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColloquially%20the%20practice%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bspringing%26quot%3B%20forward%20and%20%26quot%3Bfalling%26quot%3B%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clamor%20has%20increased%20in%20recent%20years%20to%20make%20DST%20permanent%2C%20especially%20among%20politicians%20and%20lobbyists%20from%20the%20Northeast%2C%20where%20frigid%20conditions%20are%20normal%20in%20the%20early%20winter%20mornings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20straightforward.%20Cutting%20back%20on%20the%20sun%20during%20the%20fall%20and%20winter%20is%20a%20drain%20on%20the%20American%20people%20and%20does%20little%20to%20nothing%20to%20help%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubio%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20ahead%20of%20the%20vote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20time%20we%20retire%20this%20tired%20tradition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubio%20said%20the%20United%20States%20sees%20an%20increase%20in%20heart%20attacks%20and%20road%20accidents%20in%20the%20week%20that%20follows%20the%20changing%20of%20the%20clocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20changes%20would%20be%20unlikely%20to%20affect%20Hawaii%20and%20most%20of%20Arizona%2C%20the%20Navajo%20Nation%2C%20American%20Samoa%2C%20Guam%2C%20the%20Northern%20Mariana%20Islands%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%20and%20the%20US%20Virgin%20Islands%2C%20which%20do%20not%20spring%20forward%20in%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734145800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F8ktuhqt_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_30_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finconvenient-donald-trump-plans-to-end-costly-daylight-saving-time-in-us-7244802%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20Friday%20he%20would%20work%20to%20end%20the%20%26quot%3Binconvenient%26quot%3B%20custom%20of%20moving%20clocks%20forward%20one%20hour%20every%20spring%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20imposing%20an%20unnecessary%20financial%20burden%20on%20the%20United%20States.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20To%20Respond%20To%20Constitution%20Debate%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%20Today%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20scheduled%20to%20reply%20on%20the%20ongoing%20Constitution%20debate%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20initiated%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Singh%2C%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20Opposition%2C%20said%20that%20some%20peop