3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fallu-arjuns-actions-led-to-incident-hyderabad-cops-on-theatres-letter-7242202%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAllu%20Arjun%3C%2Fa%3E's%20lawyer%20Ashok%20Reddy%20said%20that%20the%20actor's%20arrest%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Billegal%20detention%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20jail%20authorities%20did%20not%20release%20him%20despite%20receiving%20an%20order%20copy%20from%20the%20Telangana%20High%20Court%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20received%20an%20order%20copy%20from%20the%20High%20Court%20but%20despite%20that%2C%20they%20didn't%20release%20him...They%20will%20have%20to%20answer.%20This%20is%20an%20illegal%20detention.%20We%20will%20take%20legal%20action...As%20of%20now%2C%20he%20has%20been%20released%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllu%20Arjun%20was%20arrested%20from%20his%20house%20in%20Jubilee%20Hills%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Friday%2C%20hours%20after%20he%20returned%20from%20Delhi%20after%20attending%20the%20success%20meet%20of%20'Pushpa%202'.%20A%20lower%20court%20had%20remanded%20him%20to%2014-day%20judicial%20custody.%20Shortly%20after%2C%20the%20Telangana%20High%20Court%20granted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fallu-arjun-arrested-pushpa-2-stampede-case-shah-rukh-khan-raees-in-allu-arjuns-pushpa-2-stampede-death-bail-case-srk-and-raees-mention-7240920%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterim%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20four%20weeks%2C%C2%A0citing%20his%20right%20to%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20couldn't%20be%20detained%20just%20because%20he's%20an%20actor...he%20cannot%20be%20held%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20was%20told%20to%20approach%20the%20lower%20court%20for%20regular%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Pushpa%202'%20Stampede%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%204%2C%20a%20stampede%20broke%20out%20at%20a%20theatre%20in%20Hyderabad%20screening%20'Pushpa%202'%20when%20Allu%20Arjun%20made%20what%20the%20police%20called%20an%20%26quot%3Bunscheduled%26quot%3B%20visit%20to%20the%20auditorium.%20A%20woman%20was%20killed%20and%20her%20son%20was%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hyderabad%20police%20had%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20Allu%20Arjun%2C%20his%20security%20team%2C%20and%20the%20management%20of%20the%20theatre%2C%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20the%20victim's%20husband.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20there%20was%20no%20intimation%20from%20the%20theatre%20management%20or%20the%20actor's%20team%20that%20they%20would%20be%20visiting%20the%20theatre.%20The%20theatre%20management%20also%20did%20not%20make%20any%20additional%20provisions%20regarding%20security%20to%20manage%20the%20crowd%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theatre%20owner%2C%20general%20manager%2C%20and%20security%20manager%20were%20arrested%20on%20December%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20hours%20after%20Allu%20Arjun%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20yesterday%2C%20the%20victim's%20husband%20defended%20the%20actor%20and%20said%20that%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20withdraw%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20ready%20to%20withdraw%20the%20case.%20I%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20arrest.%20Allu%20Arjun%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20stampede%20in%20which%20my%20wife%20passed%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EReactions%20pour%20in%20on%20Allu%20Arjun's%20arrest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20politicians%20and%20people%20from%20the%20film%20industry%20came%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Allu%20Arjun%20and%20slammed%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBRS%20leader%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Telangana%2C%20calling%20the%20action%20against%20the%20actor%20a%20%26quot%3Bpinnacle%20of%20insecurity%20of%20rulers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20totally%20sympathise%20with%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20stampede%20but%20who%20failed%20really%3F%20Treating%20Allu%20Arjun%20as%20a%20common%20criminal%20is%20uncalled%20for%20especially%20for%20something%20he%20isn't%20directly%20responsible.%20There%20is%20always%20space%20for%20respect%20and%20dignified%20conduct.%20I%20strongly%20condemn%20high-handed%20behaviour%20of%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Farrest-of-allu-arjun-proves-congress-against-creative-industry-union-minister-ashwini-vaishnaw-7242975%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAshwini%20Vaishnaw%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20the%20stampede%20incident%20a%20%26quot%3Bpoor%20arrangement%20by%20the%20state%20and%20local%20administration%26quot%3B.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20Congress%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20respect%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20creative%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...The%20arrest%20of%20Allu%20Arjun%20proves%20it%20yet%20again.%20The%20mishap%20at%20Sandhya%20Theatre%20was%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20poor%20arrangements%20by%20the%20state%20and%20local%20administration.%20Now%2C%20to%20deflect%20that%20blame%2C%20they%20are%20indulging%20in%20such%20publicity%20stunts.%20The%20Telangana%20Government%20should%20assist%20those%20affected%20and%20punish%20those%20making%20the%20arrangements%20that%20day%20instead%20of%20continuously%20attacking%20film%20personalities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734144660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fblli6tj8_allu-arjun_625x300_14_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fallu-arjun-arrested-after-pushpa-2-screening-stampede-released-from-jail-7244419%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20woman%20had%20died%20in%20the%20stampede%20on%20December%204%20-%20triggered%20by%20the%20actor%20turning%20up%20at%20the%20city's%20Sandhya%20Theatre%20for%20a%20special%20scre