Trump%20On%20Mystery%20Drone%20Sightings%20Across%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20called%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bshooting%20down%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20mystery%20drones%20that%20have%20been%20appearing%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20drones%20were%20first%20spotted%20in%20New%20Jersey%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20and%20are%20now%20being%20seen%20in%20other%20areas%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%20and%20the%20White%20House%20have%20so%20far%20maintained%20that%20these%20do%20not%20pose%20any%20national%20security%20threat%20and%20nor%20there%20is%20any%20evidence%20of%20a%20foreign%20hand%20in%20it.%20The%20appearance%20of%20the%20mystery%20drones%2C%20however%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20subject%20of%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMystery%20Drone%20sightings%20all%20over%20the%20Country.%20Can%20this%20really%20be%20happening%20without%20our%20government's%20knowledge%3F%20I%20don't%20think%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20on%20Friday%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20a%20social%20media%20platform%20owned%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F113647906240301335%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20the%20public%20know%2C%20and%20now.%20Otherwise%2C%20shoot%20them%20down!!!%20DJT%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20with%20his%20personal%20signature%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20on%20Thursday%20said%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20yet%20that%20the%20reported%20drone%20sightings%20pose%20a%20national%20security%20or%20a%20public%20safety%20threat%20or%20that%20they%20have%20a%20foreign%20nexus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20and%20the%20FBI%20are%20investigating%20these%20sightings%2C%20working%20closely%20with%20state%20and%20local%20law%20enforcement%20to%20provide%20resources%2C%20using%20numerous%20detection%20methods%20to%20better%20understand%20their%20origin%2C%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Communications%20Advisor%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20%26quot%3B...%20upon%20review%20of%20available%20imagery%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20many%20of%20the%20reported%20sightings%20are%20actually%20manned%20aircraft%20that%20are%20being%20operated%20lawfully.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20Coast%20Guard%20is%20providing%20support%20to%20the%20State%20of%20New%20Jersey%20and%20has%20confirmed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20any%20foreign-based%20involvement%20from%20coastal%20vessels.%20And%2C%20importantly%2C%20there%20are%20no%20reported%20or%20confirmed%20drone%20sightings%20in%20any%20restricted%20airspace%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20and%20FBI%20also%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20yet%20that%20the%20reported%20drone%20sightings%20pose%20a%20national%20security%20or%20a%20public%20safety%20threat%20or%20have%20a%20foreign%20nexus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20supporting%20local%20law%20enforcement%20in%20New%20Jersey%20with%20numerous%20detection%20methods%20but%20have%20not%20corroborated%20any%20of%20the%20reported%20visual%20sightings%20with%20electronic%20detection.%20To%20the%20contrary%2C%20upon%20review%20of%20available%20imagery%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20many%20of%20the%20reported%20sightings%20are%20actually%20manned%20aircraft%2C%20operating%20lawfully.%20There%20are%20no%20reported%20or%20confirmed%20drone%20sightings%20in%20any%20restricted%20air%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20DHS%2C%20FBI%20and%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%2C%20Senator%20Kirsten%20Gillibrand%2C%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20and%20Senators%20Cory%20Booker%20and%20Andy%20Kim%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bsince%20late%20November%2C%20communities%20in%20the%20New%20York%20City%20area%20and%20northern%20New%20Jersey%20have%20reported%20several%20incidents%20of%20unattributable%20drone%20sightings%20at%20night%2C%20alarming%20both%20residents%20and%20local%20law%20enforcement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20highlighted%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20potential%20safety%20and%20security%20risks%20posed%20by%20these%20drones%20in%20civilian%20areas%20is%20especially%20pertinent%20considering%20recent%20drone%20incursions%20at%20sensitive%20military%20sites%20in%20and%20outside%20of%20the%20continental%20United%20States%20over%20the%20past%20year%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongressman%20Josh%20Gottheimer%20from%20New%20Jersey%20on%20Friday%20urged%20federal%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20led%20by%20the%20FBI%20and%20DHS%2C%20to%20allow%20state%20and%20local%20law%20enforcement%20to%20deploy%20assets%20that%20can%20safely%20take%20down%20drones%20that%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20be%20in%20our%20skies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20FBI%2C%20DHS%20and%20the%20FAA%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20immediately%20brief%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20also%20need%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20state%20and%20local%20law%20enforcement%20to%20give%20them%20the%20equipment%20they%20need%20to%20monitor%20drone%20activity.%20There%20is%20clearly%20too%20much%20of%20it%20here%20in%20Jersey%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Gottheimer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734138960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fo37c91h8_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_10_Decem