%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20cautioned%20the%20United%20States%20in%20his%20speech%20at%20that%20meeting%20while%20he%20spoke%20about%20tariff%20hikes%2C%20tech-bans%2C%20and%20trade%20clampdowns%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20vowed%20to%20impose%20on%20China%20once%20he%20takes%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20such%20war%20of%20words%20and%20aggressive%20posturing%20by%20both%20Trump%20and%20Xi%2C%20the%20former's%20decision%20to%20invite%20the%20Chinese%20President%20for%20his%20inauguration%20ceremony%20does%20indeed%20seem%20both%20misplaced%20and%20rather%20unusual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20has%20blown%20hot%20and%20cold%20in%20his%20views%20about%20Xi%20Jinping%20-%20calling%20him%20%26quot%3Ba%20brilliant%20guy%26quot%3B%20on%20one%20occasion%2C%20and%20describing%20him%20as%20his%20nemesis%20on%20another.%20An%20invite%20sent%2C%20as%20one%20would%2C%20to%20an%20ally%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20calling%20China%20%26quot%3Bthe%20greatest%20threat%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20President%20Xi%20in%20his%20pre-election%20podcast%20with%20Joe%20Rogan%2C%20Trump%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20controls%201.4%20billion%20people%20with%20an%20iron%20fist.%20I%20mean%2C%20he's%20a%20brilliant%20guy%2C%20whether%20you%20like%20it%20or%20not.%26quot%3B%20But%20in%20two%20other%20interviews%20he%20called%20Xi%20Jinping%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20threat%20to%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20and%20labelled%20China%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20of%20the%20century%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20has%20also%20appointed%20Marco%20Rubio%20as%20his%20Secretary%20of%20State%20and%20Mike%20Walz%20as%20his%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20-%20both%20staunch%20critics%20of%20China%20who%20have%20kept%20a%20hawk's%20eye%20on%20every%20move%20Beijing%20makes%20-%20so%20much%20so%2C%20that%20the%20Chinese%20government%20has%20placed%20sanctions%20on%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%20and%20in%202020%20had%20banned%20him%20fr