vorites%20this%20season%20are%20oversized%20wool%20coats%20and%20long%2C%20tailored%20fleece%20jackets.%3Cp%3EJ.Crew%2C%20Madewell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20warm%20winter%20coat%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20frumpy.%20If%20you're%20attending%20winter%20weddings%2C%20holiday%20parties%2C%20or%20apr%C3%A8s%20ski%20events%2C%20you'll%20want%20an%20outer%20layer%20that's%20equal%20parts%20polished%20and%20snug.%20The%20best%20winter%20dress%20coats%20elevate%20your%20outfit%20while%20keeping%20the%20frigid%20air%20at%20bay.%20Features%20like%20high%20collars%2C%20hoods%2C%20fleece%20lining%2C%20and%20belts%20add%20warmth%20and%20style.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBelow%20is%20a%20curated%20guide%20to%20stylish%20and%20warm%20winter%20dress%20coats%2C%20including%20a%20handful%20we%20tested%20ourselves.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20style%20these%20coats%20for%20formal%20events%2C%20and%20they%20still%20protected%20us%20from%20the%20cold%20and%20wind.%20Further%2C%20you'll%20find%20picks%20based%20on%20extensive%20research%20from%20customer%20reviews%2C%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20weighty%20wool%20blends%20and%20lengthy%20insulated%20jackets.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EQuince%20Italian%20Wool%20Double-Breasted%20Slouch%20Coat%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20image%20of%20a%20model%20wearing%20an%20oversized%20coat%20in%20front%20of%20a%20landscaped%20yard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6555286222cf74a57398092f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20perfectly%20oversized%20fit%2C%20the%20thing%20I%20love%20most%20about%20this%20coat%20is%20that%20it's%20lined%20on%20the%20inside%20for%20added%20warmth.%20Many%20slouch%20coats%20are%20made%20without%20a%20lining%20because%20the%20lack%20of%20added%20structure%20allows%20the%20wool%20to%20drape%20more%20loosely.%20While%20that%20may%20give%20you%20a%20slightly%20more%20cozy%20silhouette%2C%20it%20means%20you%20miss%20out%20on%20any%20real%20insulation.%20The%20lining%20here%20gives%20the%20coat%20just%20enough%20structure%20to%20feel%20sophisticated%20and%20clean%2C%20but%20clever%20details%20like%20a%20shoulder%20seam%20that%20continues%20down%20the%20arm%20still%20gives%20it%20an%20almost%20cape-like%2C%20drop-shoulder%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20personally%20recommend%20opting%20for%20the%20black%20color%20over%20the%20tan.%20While%20the%20tan%20might%20look%20nice%20in%20online%20photos%2C%20I%20can%20tell%20that%20the%20color%20is%20pretty%20flat%2C%20which%20means%20it%20won't%20look%20quite%20as%20elegant%20in%20person.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3ESally%20Kaplan%2C%20executive%20editor%2C%20Insider%20Reviews%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPatagonia%20Lonesome%20Mesa%20Long%20Coat%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%3A%20The%20co-author%20wearing%20the%20Patagonia%20Lonesome%20Mesa%20Coat%20in%20an%20outdoor%20waterfront%20setting.%20Right%3A%20Left%3A%20The%20co-author%20in%20a%20mirror%20selfie%20wearing%20the%20Patagonia%20Lonesome%20Mesa%20Coat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673b786bfa0140cdd5641013%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGabrielle%20Chase%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20dressed%20up%2C%20this%20coat%20is%20simply%20made%20for%20winter%20weddings%20%E2%80%94%20but%20being%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74501-20%26h%3D5c1c966f80ade3618db3e68db07fe4a6ca68d89016a79917f585632917822f24%26postID%3D673b76b3d4b5ffeb6fdb2d68%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fbest-winter-dress-coats-for-women%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.patagonia.com%252Fshop%252Fwomens%252Ffleece%252Fjackets%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPatagonia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20looks%20just%20as%20correct%20when%20sat%20around%20a%20campfire.%20The%20high-pile%20fleece%20material%20feels%20synthetic%20to%20the%20touch%20and%20sheds%20a%20bit%20at%20first%2C%20but%20it%20does%20its%20job%20of%20keeping%20me%20insulated.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt%20has%20elasticated%20wrist%20cuffs%20and%20a%20high%20fuzzy%20collar%20also%20help%20block%20cool%20air%20from%20coming%20in.%20Even%20in%20high%20winds%20I%20don't%20need%20a%20scarf%20when%20I%20wear%20this%20coat.%20I%20do%20however%20wish%20the%20collar%20had%20more%20structure%20to%20it%2C%20because%20it%20only%20stands%20on%20its%20own%20when%20zipped%20all%20the%20way%20up.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAnother%20great%20feature%20its%20its%20dual%20zipper.%20I%20tested%20this%20coat%20by%20wearing%20it%20while%20climbing%20stairs%20and%20riding%20a%20bike.%20Because%20I%20can%20leave%20the%20top%20half%20zipped%20and%20the%20bottom%20half%20unzipped%2C%20it%20means%20I'm%20warm%20up%20around%20my%20core%20and%20my%20legs%20can%20still%20move%20freely.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20waist%20pockets%20are%20lined%20with%20a%20hand-warming%20fabric%20and%20have%20plenty%20of%20room%20to%20carry%20your%20essentials%20if%20you%20rather%20forgo%20a%20handbag.%20Plus%2C%20there's%20a%20zippered%20interior%20chest%20pocket%20so%20you%20can%20keep%20your%20valuables%20secure%20and%20close.%20The%20Lonesome%20Mesa%20coat%20also%20comes%20in%20forest%20green%20and%20navy%2C%20but%20I%20chose%20the%20light%20beige%20because%20it's%20a%20refreshing%20switch%20from%20the%20dark%2C%20shadowy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-winter-coat-women%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewinter%20coats%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20usually%20tend%20towards%20in%20wintertime.%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3EGabrielle%20Chase%2C%20associate%20style%20editor%2C%20Insider%20Reviews%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUGG%20Gert