2%3EUnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20authorities%20put%20a%20bounty%20on%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Police%20Department's%20Crime%20Stoppers%20program%20offered%20a%20%2410%2C000%20reward%20for%20information%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20killer's%20arrest%20or%20conviction.%20The%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20followed%20suit%2C%20touting%20a%20%2450%2C000%20reward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20tipster%20who%20called%20911%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-luigi-mangione-charged-unitedhealthcare-ceo-murder-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELuigi%20Mangione%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20needs%20Mangione%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20Monday%20and%20accused%20of%20the%20killing%2C%20to%20be%20convicted%20before%20they%20get%20the%20money.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20ordinary%20Crime%20Stoppers%20reward%20is%20under%20%243%2C500.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20tipsters%20can%20be%20paid%20upon%20arrest%20and%20indictment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20when%20a%20reward%20is%20raised%20to%20exceed%20that%20amount%2C%20the%20money%20isn't%20disbursed%20until%20a%20conviction%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eeither%20at%20trial%20or%20through%20a%20guilty%20plea%2C%20%3Cspan%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Police%20Foundation%2C%20which%20administers%20the%20funds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficers%20in%20Altoona%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20arrested%20Mangione%20at%20a%20McDonald's%20restaurant%2C%20on%20charges%20that%20he%20lied%20about%20his%20identity%20and%20illegally%20carried%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-are-ghost-guns-unitedhealthcare-shooting-suspect-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eghost%20gun%3C%2Fa%3E%20police%20said%20was%20assembled%20from%203D-printed%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-luigi-mangione-indictment-extradition-psych-defense-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMangione%20will%20likely%20be%20extradited%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20New%20York%2C%20where%20a%20warrant%20indicates%20he%20will%20be%20charged%20with%20murder%2C%20among%20other%20crimes.%20Mangione%20has%20not%20made%20any%20public%20statements%20since%20his%20arrest%20and%20has%20not%20yet%20entered%20a%20plea%20for%20the%20charges%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20Dickey%2C%20an%20Altoona-based%20defense%20attorney%20representing%20Mangione%20on%20his%20Pennsylvania%20charges%2C%20didn't%20immediately%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20New%20York%20Police%20Department%20officials%2C%20the%20911%20caller%20was%20a%20fast-food%20worker%20who%20was%20tipped%20off%20about%20Mangione%20by%20a%20restaurant%20patron.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20that%20person%20didn't%20call%20Crime%20Stoppers%20directly%2C%20they%20can%20still%20potentially%20receive%20the%20reward%2C%20according%20to%20the%20foundation%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20individual%20in%20Pennsylvania%2C%20who%20called%20in%20a%20tip%2C%20is%20eligible%20to%20receive%20the%20reward%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4de5d68-569b-483e-ba7a-4d41ed660279%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20one%20person%20could%20collect%20rewards%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECrime%20Stoppers%20doesn't%20always%20pay%20out%20the%20maximum%20amount%20of%20their%20rewards.%20The%20total%20is%20determined%20by%20a%20board%20overseen%20by%20the%20foundation%2C%20which%20acts%20upon%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20commanding%20officer%20of%20the%20NYPD's%20Crime%20Stoppers%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20high%20profile%20of%20Thompson's%20killing%2C%20it's%20likely%20the%20tipster%20will%20be%20eligible%20for%20the%20full%20amount%2C%20Joe%20Giacalone%2C%20a%20former%20New%20York%20police%20officer%20who%20oversaw%20the%20unit%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20this%20was%20a%20national%20manhunt%2C%20I%20would%20assume%20they%20would%20ask%20for%20the%20highest%20amount%20of%20award%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Giacalone%2C%20now%20an%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20John%20Jay%20College%20of%20Criminal%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20would%20also%20decide%20whether%20the%20reward%20would%20go%20to%20either%20the%20restaurant%20patron%2C%20who%20first%20apparently%20recognized%20Mangione%2C%20or%20the%20employee%20who%20called%20911%2C%20or%20both.%20Those%20details%20%26quot%3Bwould%20be%20ironed%20out%20between%20Crime%20Stoppers%20and%20the%20police%20foundation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foundation%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2C%20on%20other%20cases%2C%20sometimes%20they%20both%20get%20their%20reward%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20the%20reward%20is%20split%20half-and-half.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20less%20clear%20whether%20the%20caller%20can%20get%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20FBI's%20%2450%2C000%20award%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20language%20on%20the%20FBI%20poster%20offered%20money%20for%20%26quot%3Binformation%20leading%20to%20the%20arrest%20and%20conviction%20of%20the%20individual%20responsible%20for%20this%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20also%20indicating%20it%20wouldn't%20pay%20out%20unless%20a%20conviction%20is%20reached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20FBI%20representative%20said%20tips%20from%20the%20public%20are%20among%20the%20agency's%20%26quot%3Bbest%20tools%20in%20preventing%2C%20detecting%2C%20and%20deterring%20crime.%26quot%3B%20It%20did%20not%20answer%20questions%20about%20the%20Mangione%20tipster%20or%20its%20reward%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20FBI%20maintains%20longstanding%20policy%20not%20to%20confirm%20the%20identity%20of%20individuals%20who%20assist%20the%20FBI%20by%20providing%20tips%20or%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20representative%20said%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20the%20FBI%20will%20not%20comment%20on%20whether%20reward%20money%20has%20been%20paid%20and%20to%20whom.%20The%20FBI%20takes%20this%20position%20for%20privacy%20protection%2C%20and%20to%20ensure%20the%20public's%20continued%20cooperation%20and%20incentivization%20with%20any%20future%20assistance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReward%20funds%20can%20help%20ease%20the%20financial%20burden%20of%20potential%20informants%2C%20whose%20lives%20may%20be%20transformed%20if%20they%20become%20cooperating%20witnesses%20or%20ultimately%20testify%20at%20trial.%20Former%20prosecutor%20Opher%20Shweiki%20said%20they%20were%20helpful%20in%20capturing%20and%20building%20the%20case%20against%20Ahmed%20Abu%20Khatallah%2C%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20the%202012%20Benghazi%20terrorist%20attack.%20The%20case%20was%20featured%20as%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BSuccess%20Stories%26quot%3B%20from%20Rewards%20for%20Justice%2C%20a%20law%20enforcement%20program%20that%20works%20with%20the%20FBI%20to%20offer%20rewards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20sometimes%20upending%20their%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shweiki%2C%20now%20a%20national%20security%20partner%20at%20Akin%20Gump.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20there's%20a%20lot%20that%20goes%20into%20that%20equation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20conviction%20in%20the%20Thompson%20killing%20could%20take%20a%20long%20time%20if%20it%20happens%20at%20all.%20As%20Business%20Insider's%20Laura%20Italiano%20reported%2C%20a%20savvy%20lawyer%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-luigi-mangione-indictment-extradition-psych-defense-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelay%20the%20Pennsylvania-to-New%20York%20extradition%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20would%20be%20before%20Mangione%20would%20be%20arraigned%20on%20murder%20charges%2C%20kicking%20off%20the%20formal%20process%20for%20the%20criminal%20case.%3C%2Fp