C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuick%20context%3A%20It%20is%20not%20unusual%20for%20big%20companies%20and%20very%20rich%20people%20to%20donate%20lots%20of%20money%20to%20presidential%20inaugurations%2C%20whether%20via%20cash%2C%20in-kind%20contributions%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20US%20elections%20themselves%20have%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-260-million-spending-trump-republican-party-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%3C%2Fa%3E)%20rules%20about%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20people%20and%20companies%20can%20spend%20on%20candidates%2C%20there's%20no%20cap%20on%20what%20they%20can%20spend%20on%20inaugural%20committees.%20The%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fec.gov%2Fhelp-candidates-and-committees%2Fpresidential-transition-and-inauguration%2Ffunding-inaugural-committee-activities%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWhile%2520donations%2520to%2520an%2520inaugural%2Cdonations%2520to%2520an%2520inaugural%2520committee.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestrictions%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20that%20the%20money%20can't%20come%20from%20foreign%20nationals%20and%20that%20the%20donations%20eventually%20have%20to%20be%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20why%20we%20can%20see%20it's%20also%20not%20unheard%20of%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opensecrets.org%2Ftrump%2Finauguration-donors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20to%20make%20inaugural%20donations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Microsoft%20kicked%20in%20%24500%2C000%20for%20Trump's%20first%20inauguration%20in%202017%3B%20Google%20spent%20%24285%2C000.%20Those%20two%20companies%20also%20contributed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2F01%2F09%2Fbiden-inaugural-donors-major-corporations-456907%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoe%20Biden's%202021%20inauguration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-corporations-president-inauguration-washingt