%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Much%20Prize%20Money%20D%20Gukesh%20Won%20After%20Becoming%20World%20Chess%20Champion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20D%20Gukesh%20created%20history%20on%20Thursday%20as%20he%20became%20the%20youngest%20world%20chess%20champion.%20Gukesh%20edged%20past%20the%20defending%20champion%20Ding%20Liren%207.5-6.5%20by%20winning%20the%2014th%20and%20last%20classical%20game%20of%20their%20World%20Championship%20tie%20in%20Singapore.%20Gukesh%20is%20now%20the%20second%20Indian%20after%20the%20great%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20to%20clinch%20this%20coveted%20title.%20The%2018-year-old%20Gukesh%20also%20dethroned%20Russian%20Grandmaster%20Garry%20Kasparov%2C%20who%20earlier%20held%20the%20record%20of%20being%20the%20youngest%20world%20champion%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Gukesh's%20prize%20money%20for%20winning%20the%20World%20Chess%20Championship%202024%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20prize%20money%2C%20victory%20in%20each%20game%20of%20the%20World%20Chess%20Championship%20was%20worth%20%24200%2C000%20(approximately%20Rs%201.69%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGukesh%20bagged%20three%20games%20and%20took%20home%20a%20whopping%20total%20of%20%24600%2C000%20(approx%20Rs%205.07%20crore).%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Liren%2C%20who%20won%20two%20games%2C%20got%20%24400%2C000%20(approx%20Rs%203.38%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20%241.5%20million%20in%20prize%20money%20will%20be%20split%20equally%20between%20the%20two%20opponents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20Gukesh's%20total%20prize%20money%20will%20be%20%241.35%20million%20(approx%20Rs%2011.45%20crore)%20while%20Liren%20will%20take%20home%20%241.15%20million%20(approx%20Rs%209.75%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20admitted%20that%20he%20didn't%20expect%20Gukesh%20to%20take%20the%20title%20home%20on%20Thursday%2C%20thinking%20the%20game%20would%20be%20decided%20in%20a%20tie-breaker%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20little%20bit%20historic%20and%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20surprise.%20Historic%20because%20he%20is%20the%20youngest%20world%20champion%20in%20history.%20Surprise%20because%2020%20minutes%20before%20the%20end%2C%20it%20didn't%20look%20like%20it%20(the%20championship%20title)%20is%20going%20to%20be%20decided%20today.%20We%20thought%20there%20would%20be%20a%20tiebreaker.%20A%20very%20very%20pleasant%20surprise%2C%26quot%3B%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20said%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20Gukesh's%20biggest%20strength%2C%20Anand%20said%20that%20he%20has%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20do%20well%20in%20everything.%20You%2C%20as%20a%20person%2C%20grow%20and%20overcome%20all%20the%20challenges.%20He%20managed%20to%20do%20that.%20He%20was%20very%20focused%20and%20dedicated.%20He%20was%20rewarded%20for%20that%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chess%20icon%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734097080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Famps3aeg_d-gukesh-afp_625x300_13_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fhow-much-prize-money-d-gukesh-won-after-becoming-world-chess-champion-7238310%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20D%20Gukesh%20created%20history%20on%20Thursday%20as%20he%20became%20the%20youngest%20world%20chess%20champion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A85%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fhow-much-prize-money-d-gukesh-won-after-becoming-world-chess-champion-7238310%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Niger's%20military%20rulers%20suspend%20BBC%20broadcasts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734096790000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F102