ideo%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20Anubhav%20encourages%20you%20to%20wander%20around.%20The%20area%20is%20known%20for%20its%20gastronomy.%20Delectable%20evidence%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Echole%20bhature%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chickpea%20gravy%20served%20with%20Indian%20flatbread)%2C%20fresh%20fruit%20%3Cem%3Echaat%3C%2Fem%3E%20(street%20food)%2C%20cooling%20%3Cem%3Edahi%20bhalle%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20dish%20that%20combines%20fluffy%20lentil%20dumplings%20soaked%20in%20creamy%20%3Cem%3Eyogurt%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20topped%20with%20spices%20and%20%3Cem%3Echutneys%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F259515%2Findian-food-recipes-pakora-map-of-india-cuisine-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epaneer%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebread%20%3Cem%3Epakoda%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(fried%20snack%20with%20cottage%20cheese).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20The%20Embassy%20Restaurant%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmbassy%20is%20independent%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20restaurant%20started%20in%201948.%20And%20food%20blogger%20Anushka%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20family%20are%20loyalists.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere%20when%20I%20was%20a%20kid.%20What%20excited%20me%20more%20than%20anything%20else%20was%20their%20size%3B%20they%20were%20so%20huge!%20I%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20I%20tasted%20the%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20the%20huge%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F313009%2Fbengaluru-couple-nidhi-shikhar-start-samosa-singh-brand-of-crispy-chaat-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejumbo-sized%20snack%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20more%20than%20what%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20could%20finish%20together!%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-