gles%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20any%20other%20home-grown%20filmmaker%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20working%20on%20content%20like%20this.%20People%20talk%20a%20lot%20about%20supporting%20such%20stories%20but%20rarely%20step%20up%20to%20fund%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20her%20journey%20of%20hardships%20and%20resilience%2C%20Indira%20has%20reached%20a%20place%20where%20she%20now%20embraces%20challenges%2C%20determined%20to%20find%20solutions%20along%20the%20way.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20blessed%20by%20the%20Almighty%20with%20the%20courage%20to%20pursue%20a%20successful%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20took%20over%20the%20spotlight%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20making%20of%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20an%20intense%20experience%20for%20everyone%20involved.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20crew%20worked%20tirelessly%2C%20often%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20to%20make%20this%20film%20what%20it%20is%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Indira.%20Looking%20back%2C%20she%20feels%20the%20struggles%20shaped%20her%20in%20ways%20she%E2%80%99ll%20always%20cherish.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20road%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%2C%20but%20the%20depth%20of%20self-made%20success%20is%20something%20I%E2%80%99ll%20always%20carry%20with%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndira%20and%20her%20team%20screened%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20the%20prestigious%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMarch%C3%A9%20du%20Film%20%3C%2Fem%3E(or%20Cannes%20Film%20Market).%20Though%20the%20film%20was%20screened%20out%20of%20competition%2C%20the%20response%20was%20moving.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20emotionally%20overwhelmed%20and%20cried%20when%20I%20turned%20back%20to%20see%20the%20audience%20appreciating%20the%20film.%20Many%20international%20filmmakers%20and%20scriptwriters%20approached%20me%20to%20discuss%20it%2C%20as%20they%20wanted%20to%20know%20more%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Indira.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-500x889.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indira%20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20March%C3%A9%20du%20Film%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-500x889.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-169x300.jpg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-150x267.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433.jpg%20620w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388047%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIndira%20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20March%C3%A9%20du%20Film%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPutul%20is%20a%20home-grown%20film%20with%20no%20foreign%20collaboration%2C%20and%20receiving%20a%20standing%20ovation%20during%20its%20screening%20in%20a%20mid-sized%20theatre%20was%20purely%20magical.%20Hearing%20praise%20from%20esteemed%20filmmakers%20like%20Aniruddha%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20and%20Margaret%20Zambonini%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20Ardenslate%20(a%20script%20development%20company)%2C%20was%20an%20unforgettable%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20occasion%2C%20Indira%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20mainstream%20films%20with%20big%20stars%20were%20struggling%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20the%20seven%20Indian%20films%20screened%20at%20Cannes%20brought%20pride%20and%20joy%20to%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20films%20that%20represented%20India%20%E2%80%94%20Indira%20herself%20carried%20her%20culture%20to%20the%20global%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CIndira%20being%20Indira%2C%20honoured%20her%20roots%20and%20culture%20even%20on%20an%20international%20stage%20like%20Cannes.%20She%20began%20her%20speech%20in%20Bangla%20before%20switching%20to%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sayan%20fondly%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%E2%80%99s%20poster%20and%20teaser%20were%20also%20launched%20at%20Cannes%2C%20and%20Sayan%20recounts%20the%20surreal%20moment%20when%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F133350%2Fbhanu-athaiya-unsung-woman-won-indias-1st-oscar-long-ar-rahman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20R%20Rahman%3C%2Fa%3E%20promoted%20the%20film.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20someone%20from%20the%20music%20industry%2C%20having%20Rahman%20acknowledge%20a%20film%20you%20have%20worked%20on%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20has%20earned%20international%20acclaim%20%E2%80%94%20is%20surreal%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sayan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayan%20stood%20as%20a%20pillar%20of%20constant%20support%20throughout%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20to%20name%20one%20person%20who%20stood%20by%20me%20and%20my%20work%2C%20it%20would%20be%20Sayan%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Indira.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20the%20director%2C%20who%20is%20always%20acknowledging%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20crew%2C%20needs%20appreciation%20too.%20Sayan%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20helping%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20achieve%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20what%E2%80%99s%20next%2C%20Indira%20is%20already%20working%20on%20a%20new%20Hindi%20project%2C%20a%20biopic%20featuring%20Divya%20Dutta%20and%20Neeraj%20Kabi%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20works%20of%20legendary%20filmmaker%20Shyam%20Benegal.%20Meanwhile%2C%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20set%20to%20be%20screened%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20aspiring%20filmmakers%2C%20Indira%20has%20some%20simple%20yet%20powerful%20advice%3A%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20let%20your%20background%20hold%20you%20back.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20be%20a%20filmmaker%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20wait%20for%20the%20right%20moment.%20Just%20grab%20a%20camera%2C%20step%20out%20of%20your%20comfort%20zone%2C%20and%20start%20filming.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Indira%20Dhar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EMukkherjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734060600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-3_11zon-1733817580.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D387993%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indira%20Dhar%20Mukkherjee%E2%80%99s%20debut%20film%2C%20Putul%2C%20journeyed%20from%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20streets%20to%20Cannes%2C%20earning%20a%20standing%20ovation.%20A%20single%20mother%2C%20Indira%20battled%20funding%20struggles%2C%20sold%20her%20jewellery%2C%20and%20balanced%20parenthood%20to%20bring%20this%20powerful%20story%20to%20life.%20Her%20resilience%2C%20rooted%20in%20her%20passion%20for%20storytelling%2C%20turned%20obstacles%20into%20triumphs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F387993%2Findira-dhar-putul-journey-cannes-success-filmmaking%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20in%20'direct%20contact'%20with%20Syrian%20rebels%20and%20hopes%20to%20keep%20military%20bases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734058440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F12%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-syria-rebel-damascus_6774558.jpg%3F20241213044317%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frussia-in-direct-contact-with-rebel-group-and-hopes-to-maintain-military-bases-in