e%20and%20commitment%20to%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20model%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F236549%2Fbihar-farmer-earns-lakhs-superfood-makhana-entrepreneur-lotus-seeds-fox-nuts-cultivation-farming-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommitment%20to%20empowering%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20working%20with%20local%20farmers%20already%20practising%20organic%20farming%2C%20they%20introduced%20a%20buyback%20model%2C%20ensuring%20that%20farmers%20could%20sell%20their%20produce%20at%20premium%20prices%2C%20far%20above%20what%20they%20would%20receive%20in%20conventional%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20partnering%20with%20Sreshte%2C%20I%20struggled%20to%20sell%20my%20organic%20mangoes%20at%20fair%20prices%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Maha%20Lakshman%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Agiripalli%2C%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Krishna%20district.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20doubling%20my%20earnings%20and%20more%20committed%20to%20organic%20farming.%20I%20would%20earn%20just%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20my%20organic%20produce%20in%20the%20conventional%20market.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%204%20lakh%20in%20just%20one%20season.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maha%20Lakshman%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Agiripalli%2C%20doubled%20his%20income%20by%20selling%20organic%20mangoes%20through%20Sreshte%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20240522-WA0036-1-1733381085-